  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>You deftly block attacks with your shield while moving through battle.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Shield Focus, base attack bonus +6 or fighter level 4th.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>You gain a +2 bonus to your AC against attacks of opportunity.<br/><br/><b>Special</b><br/>Defended Movement counts as both Dodge and Mobility for the purposes of feats that have Dodge and Mobility as prerequisites.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>You can spend 3 stamina points as an immediate action to increase the bonus to your AC to +4 against a single attack. (See page 18.)",
